Expectations are added by calling Server::expect⟨8⟩. Every invocation of expect appends a new expectation onto the list. Expectations are only removed from the server on Drop or when Server::verify_and_clear⟨9⟩ is invoked. This guarantees that all expectations are always verified.
Expectations consist of:
